{"tid":1659752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「公投」建議訂立721為香港港殤紀念日","createTime":"2019-10-17T06:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T07:32:11.000Z","uid":60562,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce323a73e453602bd7ed119a324b6e16fe9eb2da","tid":1659752,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:30:46.000Z","msg":"由於身在藍營心在黃既張司長提醒<br />\n我認為香港市民應永遠不要忘記<br />\n2019年7月21日<br />\n呢一日係香港立港而黎<br />\n發生最大型恐怖襲擊既日子<br />\n香港人應永永遠遠要記住<br />\n香港曾經有幾腐敗<br />\n警黑勾結有幾嚴重<br />\n讓我到光復成功<br />\n亦唔可以忘記以前黑暗既日子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同請正評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不認同請負評<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 同理10月1日亦應定為南丫海難港殤日"},{"pid":"4960338160d08cb9f03a3a18f79aae6c15aab413","tid":1659752,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:30:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54a2364013039c9d9d502afac664650d0ff81b77","tid":1659752,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:31:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3dc79e4fd17d0ba1235ece9e158170d0e2b6de84","tid":1659752,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"e61a70f87b737728c12ea7d50a9d7e1d4178ae44","tid":1659752,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:31:29.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"b1f8ee5662e135bee7e63e9f3de066c0e16d48ab","tid":1659752,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"d9cf2e51f3cc2e6fcb9f64874abf7576bf705773","tid":1659752,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:31:52.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"8a8b01eaab27223d61c66be875cd4147b24c8d47","ti